# Environment variables — copy to .env and adjust for local development.
# Never commit .env (the pre-commit hook blocks it).
#
# Secrets are resolved from Bun.secrets first, then fall back to environment
# variables with the key transformed to UPPER_SNAKE_CASE:
#   com.herdr.<service>/api-key  →  COM_HERDR_<SERVICE>_API_KEY
#
# Example for service "market-intel":
# COM_HERDR_MARKET_INTEL_API_KEY=...
# COM_HERDR_MARKET_INTEL_DB_URL=...
